Angel Prime




Angel Prime was thinking the maximals were overun easily he needed to do 
something about this. Angel Prime then had a idea. he opened up his chest 
and pulled out the maximal matrix. he walked over and put it in Ironraptors 
hands.


Angel Prime:



"I am sorry if I caused any trouble. I am going to leave for now and come 
back soon in your time. I am going on a quest threw time. I am about 17 when 
I return I will be 20. hold on to the matrix for me till I get back."



Angel Prime cloaks himself and opens up a portal only he can see he walks 
into it and he is gone.
